<P>I looked upon the bills, and telling her I could not &s;ay but the bills were very rea&s;onable: but that I was &s;orry to tell her, I feared I mu&s;t be her lowe&s;t cu&s;tom|er. With all my heart, &s;aid &s;he, I have ten to one as many of them as the other; and then, &s;aid &s;he, if the child be dead born, or &s;hould not live, you &s;ave the
<PB N="49" REF="049057_0048_10264DA9F5183D48">
